    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for all your adventures? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the 'brand new' price tag. It runs beautifully and is super comfy for those long commutes or weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies. The double-VANOS system has been serviced for optimal cam timing, and the chassis is stabilized by Bilstein dampers and reinforced subframe mounting points. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul, ensuring the mechanical vitals remain robust despite minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
