    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior is finished in a deep charcoal metallic that still retains a brilliant luster; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper, the body panels are straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The black leather seats show light, natural creasing on the driver's bolster but remain firm and comfortable, while the dashboard and touchpoints are free of any sun damage or sticky residues. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the premium infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains quiet over bumps. It sits on a set of high-quality all-season tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 36500.0,
