      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine and a precise 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. The naturally aspirated powerplant delivers 320 hp with a linear torque curve, supported by a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and documented rear main seal replacement. The chassis retains its signature communicative feedback through the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering, while the suspension geometry remains tight for spirited cornering. Finished in a classic palette, the exterior shows minor road-use patina, but the mechanical vitals\u2014including the Bosch Motronic DME mapping and four-piston monobloc calipers\u2014are in excellent working order. This is a mechanically sound, high-revving 911 ready for the apex.",
